'''''A Elbereth Gilthoniel!'' 1, no. 2''' is an issue of the fanzine/newsletter ''A Elbereth Gilthoniel!'' published by the Fellowship of Middle Earth (a [[Tolkien fandom|Tolkien fan-group]] at [[Wikipedia:Monash University|Monash University]]). Included is an article containing the first 19 lines of [[J.R.R. Tolkien]]'s poem "[[Visio de Doworst|Doworst]]" (p. 3).<ref name=RG>{{CG|RG}}, p. 214</ref><ref name=DA>[[Douglas A. Anderson]], "R. W. Chambers and ''The Hobbit''", in {{TS|3}}, p. 144</ref><ref name=TB>{{webcite|author=|articleurl=http://www.tolkienbooks.net/php/details.php?reference=63510|articlename=A Elbereth Gilthoniel. 1978|dated=|website=TB|accessed=4 March 2012}}</ref><ref name=Guide>{{webcite|author=|articleurl=http://www.tolkienguide.com/modules/wiwimod/index.php?page=AElbereth2-78|articlename=A Elbereth Gilthoniel! #2 (1978)|dated=7 July 2011|website=Guide|accessed=4 March 2012}}</ref>

The newsletter was likely released in the month of June [[1978]]<ref group="note">The newsletter references a prior meeting on May 26th and an upcoming meeting on July 1st.</ref>
